      "text": "Tai Deblei irr diwi Mei-\ntas/ Dohd schurp/ dohd schurp : \nSchihs trihs Leetas ne tohp pee-\nehdinatas/ un tas zettortts nefak-\nka: Gann irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Elle/ Tahs Geewas\nne.augliga Mahte/ ta Senme/\nfo ar ühdeni ne warr pildiht/ un\ntas Uggunê ne fakka: Gann irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Azz/ kas to Tehwu\napsmeij/ un lcedsahs tat Mah-\ntei flauiiht/ to pazchu isknahps\ntee Krankti pee Uppes / un tee\njauni Ehrgti to ehdihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schihs trihs Leetas irr\nman wiﬀat brihntigas/ un to zet-\ntortu es ne vahrsinnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Ehrcta Zetsch Debbe-\nsis/ Tschubskas Zetsch us Akini-\nna Kalnu/ Laiwas Zettsch Juhfas\nWiddû/ un ta Wihra Zetsch pee\nweenas Meitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta patt irr tas Zetsch\nweenas Geewas/ kas to Lauilbu\npahrkahpj/ winna ehd un flanka\ntawu Mutti/ un fakka : Es ne\nefmu Netaifnibu padarrtjsti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahr trim Leetahm kusti-\nnajabs ta Semme/ un to zettor-\ntu winna ne mahē panest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahr weenu Kalpu / kad\ntas par Walditaju tohp/ un pahr\nweenu Seeki/ kad tam leeka Mai-\nfe irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahr eenihdetu Geewu/\nkad ta prezzeta tohp / un pahr\nweenu Kalpont/ kad ta farwas\nGaspraschas Mantneeze tohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee tschetri irr u\nwirs Senmes/ un tomehr g\nraki neka tee Gudree.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tahs Skudas weens\nspehzigs Pulks/ tomehr fat-\ntahs jawu Barribu Waffard\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Kaninkeni weena\nspehziga Tauta/ tomehr leek\njawas Nammus Akmina-K\nnôs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teem Sisteneem ne\nKehninsch / tomehr iseet wi-\nwift itt ka Karrogds dallitti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sirnekslis ausch ar ab\njahm Rohkahm/ un irr Kehni\nPillis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Scheem trim irr la-\nStafgafchana/ un tas zettort-\neet gann slagdr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weens wezz Lauwa tw\nreus starp teein Swehreem / t\nne weenam Galwit greech.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weens Kurtê/ kam la-\nGurni irr/ jeb weens Ahsis:\nweens Kehninsch prett ko\nweens drihgst zeltees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Effi tu Gekibn dsiu\nun lepnigi turrejees / un effi\ntaunas Leetas padohinajs / t\nleez to Rohku us Mutti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta Peenu Kehrnesch\nna isdohd Sweestu/ un Deg-\nnu Schraukichana isspeesch Q\nint/ un kas to Bahrsibu kar-\nna/ tas pazelt Kildu.\n"
    }
